{"word":"οὐμήν","slug":"οὐμήν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>οὐμήν</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>not however</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; —<el>οὐ μὴν οὐδέ</el> <i>not at all however</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>οὐ μὴν . . γε</el> after a negative, <i>no nor even yet</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>nedum</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}